News.Title: Chandan Healthcare Wins ₹260 Cr Punjab PPP Project
News.Summary: Chandan Healthcare secures a significant 10-year public-private partnership project in Punjab valued at ₹260 million, marking a major business development for the healthcare company.

News.Title: Chandan Healthcare Partners with Jeena Sikho in Punjab
News.Summary: Chandan Healthcare has announced a strategic partnership with Jeena Sikho to enter the Punjab market, marking the company's expansion into the northern Indian state's healthcare sector.

News.Title: Chandan Healthcare: Shares List with 3.84% Premium on NSE SME
News.Summary: Chandan Healthcare shares listed at ₹165.10 on the NSE SME, representing a 3.84% premium over the issue price. The IPO had been oversubscribed by more than 7 times.
